perl-xml-regexp (Regular expressions for XML tokens)

This package contains regular expressions for the following
XML tokens: BaseChar, Ideographic, Letter, Digit, Extender,
CombiningChar, NameChar, EntityRef, CharRef, Reference, Name,
NmToken, PubidLiteral, SystemLiteral, CharRef, EntityRef, AttName,
and AttValue.

HOME: https://metacpan.org/pod/XML::RegExp

======================================================================
